          <title>SOCIAL HISTORY</title>
          <text>Tobacco: Active smoker -- currently 1/2 ppd, down from 1 ppd. Started age 21. Approximately 35 pack-years. On nicotine patch, trying to quit. Alcohol: Former heavy drinker, quit 2020. Employment: Disabled/SSDI since 2023. Marital Status: Divorced x 2. Lives alone, daughter checks daily. Home oxygen via concentrator + portable tanks. Exercise: Very limited by dyspnea. Can walk ~50 feet.</text>
